text: This app will save you from being stuck in your head! Great, team of people. It was so easy to use and very fast paced with getting me connected to someone. I am happy to find a new way to talk to someone, instead of weekend calls to the crisis center. Life just got a little better because of this app.

Most of the listeners were not online during the initial search. The chat I started with one listeners remains unreplied for days and all the notifications are from the app admins. Even saw some listeners who had sexual remarks on their listener descriptions. No filter or at least a check on the listeners at all? A great idea if it works.
replyText: Elle, we're sorry you had this frustrating experience! Please report any Listener who acts in an unprofessional manner by leaving a written review for that individual after the chat. We hope you‚Äôll return to the 7 Cups community and find a caring Listener.

7 cups has done wonders for me as a person since the passing of my mom a couple of months ago. I actually came to find a neutral Person to vent to and eventually became a listener which was better. I read the 7 cups for the searching soul and finished it in October right before my mom passed. Thank you 7 cups Creator and the people who I have had the pleasure of chatting with.

Uninstalling 7 Cups of Me or 7 Cups of Narcissists.    Wow, for a supposed "support" site be careful of the chat rooms.  They are named Anxiety Support, Depression Support, Compassion Corner and the like but don't be fooled.  It's more like Kiddie Corner where it's gossip, cliques, vulgarity, violence, you name it.  When you post something of genuine concern the useless chatter goes on.  It's pathetic, a huge waste of time sorting through all the bs talk about how much that person weighs, how this person loves Sea World, what another person's gym or facial care routine is.  OH and let's not forget the people threatening suicide or homicide.  I am happy to be leaving this very toxic, draining "support" community.  I stopped reporting people because that's all I was doing and my time is valuable.  Your toxic chat rooms are not my problem!
